<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold my-5 mx-auto">Kalmia</h1>
<p>An app to help you make sense of your chronic illness.</p>

<ul class="list-disc my-5 mx-auto">
  <li>Record information about each episode</li>
  <li>Visualize trends over time</li>
  <li>Your data is yours: only saved client-side, exportable to Excel</li>
</ul>

<p>
  Named after the <a 
  href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kalmia_latifolia"
  class="underline"
  ><i>Kalmia latifolia</i></a>, a symbol of perseverance. Also known as spoonwood, alluding to the concept of <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spoon_theory" class="underline">spoon theory</a>.
</p>